  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Space Nature Attack TD is a traditional fixed path tower defense that allows you to gain resources per map completed which are used to level up your towers and customize them to suit your own strategies!<br><br><br><i><u><strong>Customize your towers!</strong></u></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Distribute skill points among basic stats and a unique tower skill. Then select an element for the tower which will provide an additional effect such as a frost slow or faster electrical projectiles.<br><br><br><i><u><strong>Twenty-four maps across three alien planet environments with scaling difficulties!</strong></u></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each map features a unique modifier to keep gameplay fresh between different levels.<br><br>Six difficulty levels are included to provide increasing levels of challenge and <br>rewards (Including permanent bonuses!). Prepare to face invading monster types at higher difficulties.<br><br>Eight extremely difficult postgame challenge maps to put your best strategies to the test!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/77bb3c7f3508408771577bc6c2c0d2ef.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Space Nature Attack TD is a traditional fixed path tower defense that allows you to gain resources per map completed which are used to level up your towers and customize them to suit your own strategies!<br><br><br><i><u><strong>Customize your towers!</strong></u></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/5583616a767da660f891bb5852dd5284.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Distribute skill points among basic stats and a unique tower skill. Then select an element for the tower which will provide an additional effect such as a frost slow or faster electrical projectiles.<br><br><br><i><u><strong>Twenty-four maps across three alien planet environments with scaling difficulties!</strong></u></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.poster.avif?t=1709278994\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.webm?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761490/extras/db0ffa81012844cbbb60ba5f69caacfa.mp4?t=1709278994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each map features a unique modifier to keep gameplay fresh between different levels.<br><br>Six difficulty levels are included to provide increasing levels of challenge and <br>rewards (Including permanent bonuses!). Prepare to face invading monster types at higher difficulties.<br><br>Eight extremely difficult postgame challenge maps to put your best strategies to the test!",
